    list ExternalBroadcastPLMNInfo {
      description "Additional definitions from MOM:min/max-elements:0/12; PLMN-related information that is served by external NR cell. Created automatically when Xn message is received, unless it already exists. Deleted automatically. Can also be created and deleted manually. Can be created by action promoteLwNRCellRelation in NRCellCU instance. RDN is the same as for automatically created instance. When created automatically, the RDNs of these MOs are ExternalBroadcastPLMNInfo=1 to ExternalBroadcastPLMNInfo=12. RDN value is assigned based on order received over Xn. Length of RDN value is up to 2 characters for automatically created instance. Instance can be created without a preceding user-initiated transaction. Precondition: MO can be created and deleted manually, only if TermPointToGNodeB has administrativeState LOCKED.";
      key "externalBroadcastPLMNInfoId";
