    list AdditionalPLMNInfo {
      description "Additional definitions from MOM:min/max-elements:0/11;systemCreated; PLMN-related Information that can be additionally served by NR cell. Created when F1 interface is set up or configuration is updated by GNBDUFunction. Deleted when configuration is updated by GNBDUFunction. The RDNs of these MOs are AdditionalPLMNInfo=1 to AdditionalPLMNInfo=11. Length of RDN value is up to 2 characters. Instance can be created without a preceding user-initiated transaction.";
