      description "A mobility target selection mode in PCI conflicting configuration. If DISABLED, first found cell relation is selected for mobility in PCI conflict configuration. If HITRATE_BASED, target cell with higher ECGI hit-rate is selected for mobility in PCI conflict configuration. If MANUAL_BASED, target cell that EUtranCellRelation::preferredCellManual is true is selected for mobility in PCI conflict configuration. If HITRATE_MANUAL_BASED, target cell is selected based on ECGI hit-rate if it is valid. If fails, target cell EUtranCellRelation::preferredCellManual is true is selected. If MANUAL_HITRATE_BASED, target cell that EUtranCellRelation::preferredCellManual is true is selected for mobility in PCI conflict configuration. If fails, target cell with higher ECGI hit-rate is selected, first found cell relation is selected cell for mobility in PCI configuration. If ECGI hit-rate based or manual configuration based target cell selection fails, first found cell relation is selected for mobility in PCI configuration. Only applicable if PciHandling::pciConflictHandlingEnabled is true..";
